  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Government should resign in response to bizarre decisions - Anura Kumara",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "JVP leader Anurakumarathisanayake has said that public life has been plunged into chaos due to the government's decision to provide fuel only for essential services.",
        "He noted that the government had failed miserably, adding that patients could not go to the hospital and students could not go to school.",
        "The JVP leader has called on the government to step down in response to the bizarre decision."
      ],
